Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在幹什麼啊  野崎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼想都不該選那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴木對麻美子之外的女生都會毫不留情地拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:45.66,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\kf69}{\c&HB049FD&\bord2\fs54\3c&H89FFFA&\pos(890,535)\clip(747,507,747,564)\t(1,690,\clip(747,507,1032,564)}我的最佳情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為啥要用那個名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 立刻 馬上給我改掉 重頭再來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我不擅長想名字誒…o(╯□╰)o
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的職業是漫畫家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就想一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像給漫畫角色起名一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人是生活和工作完全分開主義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就野崎梅太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HB45847&}初次見面 野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是 最開始專注攻略一個角色比較輕鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要選哪個妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.54,note*,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\frz-103\fs43\c&HC652FF&\3c&HFEFFF8&\bord2\move(1055,440,1055,365,0,2000)}親切的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個有點像佐倉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎 難道你……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網上說這個角色的故事最好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在網上看劇透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9D9DE3&}怎麼了？有事情一定要告訴我哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.04,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(269,0)\pos(828,196)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}忍著不{\fn华文楷体\b1}說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.04,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(269,0)\pos(828,285)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.04,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(269,0)\pos(828,382)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}只是微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個在少女漫畫中也是王道劇情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.48,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 我發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.85,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我第一次看到你這一面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女主角會對 男主角只對她展現的柔弱的一面 而心動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發牢騷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.26,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\pos(828,196)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}忍著不{\fn华文楷体\b1}說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.26,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\pos(828,285)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.26,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\pos(828,382)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}只是微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HB0B3EC&}野崎君 你……原來是這麼小心眼的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全理解不了這個女人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 你不要再用女生的視角玩GALGAME了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且話說回來 女生看到你軟弱的一面只會失望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信你問佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這事不用打電話問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小禦禦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野…野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼晚了真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我對自己的想法產生了疑問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你還是忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5482F4&}野崎君他在示弱……？！（心動）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你為什麼不多活用下朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會告訴你好感度和其他情報的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H8996C3&}有事就來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種剛見面 就來套近乎的傢伙怎麼能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種接近主人公要做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背地裏其實是欺負主人公的大Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.73,warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\ko13}{\fs56\b1\move(1140,160,1140,189)\2a&HFF&\bord3\shad0\3c&H7A887A&}來{\ko22}\N做{\ko22}\N朋{\ko22}\N友{\ko22}\N吧{\ko70}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將她逼上絕路 讓她絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就會說出這種臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H6B52E7&}其實從第一次見到你的時候 就非常討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲主旨變了吧喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是關心戀愛的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 放心找朋友幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都說到這個份上了……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.37,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,175)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}移動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,300)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,405)\c&HFEF5FB&\3c&H746799&\4c&H746799&\bord1\shad1}{\t(1710,1710,\alpha&H80\shad0)\t(1810,1810,\alpha&H0&\shad1)\t(1877,1877,\alpha&H80\shad0)\t(1977,1977,\alpha&H0&\shad1)}去問友田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.37,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(570,650)\c&HFEFDFD&\3c&HAA689C&\bord2\b1}之後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&}那我就特別讓你看看我的情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&}到現在為止好感度是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&}送你電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼友田這麼奉獻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你有什麼好處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事怎樣都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是暗戀主人公！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這表現的多麼明顯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H3F39B7&\blur1}所以說那樣遊戲的主旨就變了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H3F39B7&\blur1}別給我把什麼事都往戀愛上扯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}有事就來找我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你一直說友田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也開始在意他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我錯了 我會認真玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之向結局努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9FA1E5&}天氣不錯呢 野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}喲 你們兩個恩恩愛愛一起上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9FA1E5&}討厭 友田君 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}我會幫你掩護的 你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}剩下的交給我 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}別放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}你不是喜歡她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}是男人就去啊 你這個蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}恭喜你畢業 三年轉眼就過去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H838EBE&\blur5}我能遇見你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友田！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然為了這種主人公浪費了三年！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也去享受青春啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我來改寫你的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們的友田得到幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！那先來決定戀愛對象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推薦這個文靜的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 禦子柴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮一下友田的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是友田會選那個妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我錯了 我根本沒有考慮到友田的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友田一定會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就開始重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於友田來說特別的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常一直在他身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會和TA一起度過假日的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友田為TA獻出青春3年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為TA付出了特別的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是主人公嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天休息 來得是不是有點早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君 我是佐倉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野崎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個怎麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熬夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熬夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.43,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起12個美少女 我還是更喜歡你啊！友田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.12,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:56.97,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明只要能默默地守護著你 就滿足了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.37,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友田……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的 這到底發生了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說等你到了我這種級別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以享受腳踏多船的樂趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是在遊戲裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小禦禦平常都不太跟女生說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是遠遠打招呼而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐倉 你深深地傷害了我的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur5\3c&H433BD3&}看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur5\3c&H433BD3&}我會把 我那具有魅惑力的聊天技巧
